						<summary>

						<p>On a stone in the front wall of the Kallinātha temple.</p>						

						<p>1488 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1410, Kīlaka, Kārttika śu. 10, corresponding to 1488 A.D. October 15 (not verifiable).</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift to the god Kallinātha of Hatrikihāḷa by Nandigauṇḍa and others.</p>						

						</summary>
